      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a strong start. To make it even more authentic to the period, can you expand on that? Maybe include some specific observations about their lack of social structure or their \"wild\" nature compared to European society? I want to really capture that sense of the explorer looking down on them as being almost animalistic or incapable of self-governance.",
